   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Go to <menucascade>
                  <uicontrol>Salesforce Setup </uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol> Security Controls </uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol> Network Access. </uicontrol>
               </menucascade>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>New.</uicontrol> Enter the IP address in the Start and End IP address fields.
</p>
            <p>
               <p>
                  <i>For the list of suggested IP ranges, see the following Adobe Sign <xref href="https://helpx.adobe.com/sign/system-requirements.html"
                           format="html"
                           scope="external">
                        <u>support article</u>
                     </xref> with their recommendations</i>.</p>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Enter the IP range and click <uicontrol>Save</uicontrol>. </p>
         </li>
